## Reproducibility\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl368\sa213\qj\partightenfactor0
\cf2 All analysis steps are documented chronologically in `supplementary_tables/extended_methods.pdf`. Frozen model objects (`.rds`) and predicted probabilities are provided to allow exact reproduction of all reported figures and tables without re-running the full pipeline. \
Random seeds used: 123 (80/20 split), 42 (LASSO CV folds), 1234 (Boruta), 7 (60/40 split and AUC bootstrap), 1234 for pooled NB; 2023 for a separate DCA bootstrap (DCA bootstrap).\
